},{"pid":"7f23d40faff7f05bbdb5bd2f37837e86c1e8cdf4","tid":421287,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T07:15:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>左膠應該唔係支持佢地獨立<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢地話支持自決<br />\n唔知係咪支持自決結果 ─ 獨立? <br />\n就唔清楚啦<br />\n<br />\n但本民青政民族黨呢連支持獨立既聯合聲明都無<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢地只係想幫手做''錫金公投''</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我覺得本民青政民族黨應該都要出聯合聲明啦<br />\n1. 同加泰一樣, 要有公投法<br />\n2. 清楚界定, 乜人先有權公投 (可以同平時選舉權唔同)<br />\n3. 多D論述公投自決獨立既權利, 補眾志朱凱廸陳志全聯合聲明譴責西班牙防暴警暴力鎮壓迴避左既野"},{"pid":"c7c9cdc82864bddc3abc31c9492f53128feeee17","tid":421287,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T07:15:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>好撚失望<br />\n<br />\n都係支持香港眾志算<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://cn.wsj.com/pictures/photo/BJ20141008092207/20.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcn.wsj.com%2Fpictures%2Fphoto%2FBJ20141008092207%2F20.jpg&h=3a7907a5&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n中箭哩排係幾高質</blockquote><br />\n黃之鋒坐監後高質左<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29695ad475c24f13f787e4aa03b43c21ce78cbf5","tid":421287,"uid":18271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T07:16:29.000Z","msg":"鄰國既事唔關香港事呀嘛"},{"pid":"4aa1b8621bdc9b9fd783d120a5309ead60e8610f","tid":421287,"uid":7323,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T07:31:34.000Z","msg":"香港就唔撚理，走去理西班牙。<br />\n關你撚事咩，扮咩有國際視野。"},{"pid":"97a69ea2896d03b41455171a5b0ef2bf0f29e98d","tid":421287,"uid":66759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T07:48:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78b86beabfd05653ef05ffb444676d6dfda2337c","tid":421287,"uid":1518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTi